Dialogue: 0.0:00:03.47.0:00:05.57.Default..0.0.0..- Hey. thanks for swinging by.\N- Yeah. no sweat.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:05.57.0:00:06.64.Default..0.0.0..We were doing a prep\Nat 26th and cal.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:06.64.0:00:07.64.Default..0.0.0..What's going on?
Dialogue: 0.0:00:07.64.0:00:08.71.Default..0.0.0..- There's been a rash of ods.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:08.71.0:00:09.71.Default..0.0.0..They're coming in in waves.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:09.71.0:00:11.31.Default..0.0.0..Third one today just coded.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:11.31.0:00:13.48.Default..0.0.0..- Heroin?\N- Yeah. but definitely laced.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:13.48.0:00:14.95.Default..0.0.0..Probably fentanyl.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:14.95.0:00:17.45.Default..0.0.0..I haven't seen anything\Nlike this since...
Dialogue: 0.0:00:17.45.0:00:18.55.Default..0.0.0..Ever.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:18.55.0:00:19.58.Default..0.0.0..- I'll put a call in\Nto narcotics...
Dialogue: 0.0:00:19.59.0:00:20.72.Default..0.0.0..See what they know.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:20.72.0:00:22.00.Default..0.0.0..- Can we get the cfd paperwork?
Dialogue: 0.0:00:22.00.0:00:23.29.Default..0.0.0..I want to see where\Nthese paramedic calls
Dialogue: 0.0:00:23.29.0:00:24.46.Default..0.0.0..are originating from.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:24.46.0:00:26.42.Default..0.0.0..- They're coming in from\Nall over the city.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:26.43.0:00:28.39.Default..0.0.0..- I've got another one.\NNarcan's wearing off.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:28.40.0:00:31.30.Default..0.0.0..- Give him another 2\Nof narcan... slow iv push.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:32.68.0:00:34.07.Default..0.0.0..All right. I'll pull together\Na detailed list when I can.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:34.07.0:00:35.33.Default..0.0.0..I got to go.\N- Thanks. man.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:35.34.0:00:36.60.Default..0.0.0..- thanks.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:38.71.0:00:41.04.Default..0.0.0..Oh. man.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:41.04.0:00:42.94.Default..0.0.0..We got to roll.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:47.41.0:00:48.45.Default..0.0.0..- What do we got?
Dialogue: 0.0:00:48.45.0:00:49.88.Default..0.0.0..- A call came in.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:49.88.0:00:52.45.Default..0.0.0..Suspicious package by the lake.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:52.45.0:00:54.95.Default..0.0.0..Family was setting up for\Ntheir kid's birthday party.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:54.95.0:00:57.86.Default..0.0.0..Roger and ashley basinski\Nover here.
Dialogue: 0.0:00:57.86.0:00:59.56.Default..0.0.0..The mother found a backpack
Dialogue: 0.0:00:59.56.0:01:01.36.Default..0.0.0..soaked in what she\Nbelieved to be blood.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:01.36.0:01:02.56.Default..0.0.0..Recovered right over here.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:02.56.0:01:04.10.Default..0.0.0..- She open it?
Dialogue: 0.0:01:04.10.0:01:06.50.Default..0.0.0..- Yeah. found a surprise inside.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:06.50.0:01:08.07.Default..0.0.0..You want to talk to 'em?\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:08.07.0:01:09.83.Default..0.0.0..- All right.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:09.84.0:01:11.60.Default..0.0.0..- All right. guys...
Dialogue: 0.0:01:24.78.0:01:25.92.Default..0.0.0..- fentanyl?
Dialogue: 0.0:01:27.05.0:01:28.55.Default..0.0.0..- 300 k worth.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:28.56.0:01:30.69.Default..0.0.0..- My guy in narcotics says\Nrecently they've been
Dialogue: 0.0:01:30.69.0:01:32.56.Default..0.0.0..pulling heroin off the streets\Nthat's been cut with it.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:32.56.0:01:34.53.Default..0.0.0..Makes it. like. 1.000 times\Nmore potent.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:34.53.0:01:36.89.Default..0.0.0..- It's killing people\Nall over chicago.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:40.63.0:01:42.43.Default..0.0.0..- Hey. sarge.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:42.44.0:01:45.94.Default..0.0.0..I heard mouse came looking\Nto get a felony dropped
Dialogue: 0.0:01:45.94.0:01:48.94.Default..0.0.0..so he could re-enlist.
Dialogue: 0.0:01:48.94.0:01:50.54.Default..0.0.0..- And if he did?
Dialogue: 0.0:01:50.54.0:01:53.08.Default..0.0.0..- I think he's carrying around\Na lot of guilt
Dialogue: 0.0:01:53.08.0:01:55.61.Default..0.0.0..that we made it home safe
Dialogue: 0.0:01:55.62.0:01:58.42.Default..0.0.0..and friends of ours didn't.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:06.63.0:02:08.13.Default..0.0.0..- grab a shoulder.\NGrab a shoulder.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:08.13.0:02:09.69.Default..0.0.0..- Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0.0:02:09.70.0:02:12.06.Default..0.0.0..Get her out of here;\Nget her to her parents.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:14.70.0:02:16.80.Default..0.0.0..- Be careful.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:19.17.0:02:21.51.Default..0.0.0..- Oh!\N- Oh. man.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:21.51.0:02:23.67.Default..0.0.0..- God.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:23.68.0:02:25.18.Default..0.0.0..- Oh. my god.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:45.20.0:02:46.50.Default..0.0.0..- Back in '06.\Nwe had freezer trucks
Dialogue: 0.0:02:46.50.0:02:47.87.Default..0.0.0..parked out back\Nfilled with stiffs
Dialogue: 0.0:02:47.87.0:02:49.73.Default..0.0.0..from all the heat-related\Ndeaths.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:49.74.0:02:51.77.Default..0.0.0..We actually ran out of toe tags.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:51.77.0:02:53.17.Default..0.0.0..- All of these are\Nfrom fentanyl?
Dialogue: 0.0:02:53.17.0:02:56.04.Default..0.0.0..- Last two weeks\Nhave been insane.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:56.04.0:02:57.78.Default..0.0.0..Dealers get the cut wrong.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:57.78.0:02:59.81.Default..0.0.0..your heart stops instantly.
Dialogue: 0.0:02:59.81.0:03:01.91.Default..0.0.0..Okay.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:01.92.0:03:05.65.Default..0.0.0..Cause of death on your doa\Nis blunt head trauma.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:05.65.0:03:08.79.Default..0.0.0..Abrasions on both shoulders
Dialogue: 0.0:03:08.79.0:03:11.69.Default..0.0.0..match the width of the backpack\Nrecovered at the scene.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:11.69.0:03:12.96.Default..0.0.0..- You find any drugs\Nin his system?
Dialogue: 0.0:03:12.96.0:03:15.03.Default..0.0.0..- Toxicology report\Ncame back clean.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:15.03.0:03:17.03.Default..0.0.0..But you may be able\Nto run with this.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:17.03.0:03:19.50.Default..0.0.0..His skin was bloated from\Nthe time in the water...
Dialogue: 0.0:03:19.50.0:03:21.57.Default..0.0.0..Ballparking at seven hours.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:21.57.0:03:23.73.Default..0.0.0..Clear as day now that\Nhe's dried out.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:29.14.0:03:30.51.Default..0.0.0..- So how's\Nthe online dating going?
Dialogue: 0.0:03:30.51.0:03:31.74.Default..0.0.0..- oh. my god. shush.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:31.74.0:03:33.01.Default..0.0.0..- Okay. sorry.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:33.01.0:03:34.55.Default..0.0.0..- can I talk to you guys?
Dialogue: 0.0:03:34.55.0:03:35.65.Default..0.0.0..- Oh. god. is that her. uh...
Dialogue: 0.0:03:35.65.0:03:37.01.Default..0.0.0..- yeah. it's her bad news voice.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:41.72.0:03:45.52.Default..0.0.0..- Julie. there's no\Neasy way to say this.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:45.53.0:03:47.59.Default..0.0.0..You're being transferred\Nback to your foot beat
Dialogue: 0.0:03:47.59.0:03:48.93.Default..0.0.0..at 26th and cal.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:48.93.0:03:50.80.Default..0.0.0..- What the hell?\NShe just got here.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:53.20.0:03:55.13.Default..0.0.0..- It's fogel.
Dialogue: 0.0:03:55.13.0:03:57.64.Default..0.0.0..- Because she didn't consent\Nto being his piece of ass?
Dialogue: 0.0:03:57.64.0:03:58.80.Default..0.0.0..- I am well aware\Nof the particulars...
Dialogue: 0.0:03:58.81.0:04:00.64.Default..0.0.0..- I mean. you got to be...\N- Burgess!
Dialogue: 0.0:04:04.51.0:04:07.55.Default..0.0.0..I brought you in at\Nmanagement discretion.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:07.55.0:04:09.08.Default..0.0.0..He went over me.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:09.08.0:04:10.95.Default..0.0.0..He went over the union.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:10.95.0:04:12.72.Default..0.0.0..He is a commander.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:12.72.0:04:16.15.Default..0.0.0..and there is nothing more\NI can do.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:16.16.0:04:17.72.Default..0.0.0..I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:17.72.0:04:19.92.Default..0.0.0..This is your last shift at 21.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:28.70.0:04:30.77.Default..0.0.0..- We'll fight it.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:39.31.0:04:41.68.Default..0.0.0..- Hey. anything come back\Non the tattoo?
Dialogue: 0.0:04:41.68.0:04:43.92.Default..0.0.0..- Yeah. I went through the\Nintake records at the morgue...
Dialogue: 0.0:04:43.92.0:04:47.65.Default..0.0.0..Checked every death certificate\Nfrom April 22. 2010...
Dialogue: 0.0:04:47.65.0:04:48.65.Default..0.0.0..By hand.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:48.66.0:04:49.69.Default..0.0.0..They're not online.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:49.69.0:04:50.82.Default..0.0.0..- So that's a no then?
Dialogue: 0.0:04:50.82.0:04:53.02.Default..0.0.0..- No.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:53.03.0:04:54.93.Default..0.0.0..It's grace clarendon.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:54.93.0:04:57.03.Default..0.0.0..Cause of death: Leukemia.
Dialogue: 0.0:04:57.03.0:04:58.23.Default..0.0.0..She was 14.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:00.10.0:05:02.05.Default..0.0.0..- Damn.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:02.05.0:05:04.00.Default..0.0.0..- Lka for her mother is\Nat the bottom of the page.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:04.00.0:05:06.14.Default..0.0.0..right hand side.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:06.14.0:05:08.07.Default..0.0.0..You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:20.35.0:05:21.79.Default..0.0.0..- theresa clarendon?
Dialogue: 0.0:05:21.79.0:05:22.89.Default..0.0.0..- Yeah.\N- I'm detective dawson.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:22.89.0:05:24.16.Default..0.0.0..This is detective olinsky.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:24.16.0:05:25.57.Default..0.0.0..- No. I asked mr. Harrison
Dialogue: 0.0:05:25.57.0:05:26.99.Default..0.0.0..to give me another week\Nto put the rent together.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:26.99.0:05:28.29.Default..0.0.0..Please don't throw me out.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:28.29.0:05:32.03.Default..0.0.0..- Uh. we're. uh...\NWe're here about your son.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:32.03.0:05:35.30.Default..0.0.0..- Why? What happened to him?
Dialogue: 0.0:05:35.30.0:05:37.07.Default..0.0.0..- Ma'am. I'm gonna\Nshow you a photo.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:42.71.0:05:44.61.Default..0.0.0..- That's his tattoo.
Dialogue: 0.0:05:48.25.0:05:50.65.Default..0.0.0..God. is he okay?
Dialogue: 0.0:05:50.65.0:05:52.25.Default..0.0.0..- Ma'am. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:03.96.0:06:07.63.Default..0.0.0..When we placed grace to rest.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:07.63.0:06:10.94.Default..0.0.0..I just assumed
Dialogue: 0.0:06:10.94.0:06:12.67.Default..0.0.0..tyler would be the one
Dialogue: 0.0:06:12.67.0:06:14.77.Default..0.0.0..to lay me next to her.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:16.34.0:06:18.04.Default..0.0.0..- Ms. Clarendon.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:18.04.0:06:21.11.Default..0.0.0..is there any chance that\Nyour son might have been
Dialogue: 0.0:06:21.11.0:06:22.98.Default..0.0.0..mixed up in something illegal?
Dialogue: 0.0:06:22.98.0:06:25.02.Default..0.0.0..- Like what?
Dialogue: 0.0:06:25.02.0:06:27.69.Default..0.0.0..- When tyler was found.\Nhe was wearing a backpack
Dialogue: 0.0:06:27.69.0:06:29.19.Default..0.0.0..filled with narcotics.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:31.96.0:06:33.96.Default..0.0.0..- Tyler had a problem with that
Dialogue: 0.0:06:33.96.0:06:36.09.Default..0.0.0..when he got back from overseas.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:36.10.0:06:38.16.Default..0.0.0..He was in the military.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:38.16.0:06:40.67.Default..0.0.0..He was trying to get\Nhis life together.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:40.67.0:06:42.13.Default..0.0.0..He got a job.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:42.14.0:06:43.70.Default..0.0.0..- Doing what?
Dialogue: 0.0:06:43.70.0:06:46.07.Default..0.0.0..- Landscaping. he said.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:46.07.0:06:47.10.Default..0.0.0..I don't know the details.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:47.11.0:06:49.07.Default..0.0.0..I saw him mostly on facebook.
Dialogue: 0.0:06:49.08.0:06:51.01.Default..0.0.0..- He have any recent posts?
Dialogue: 0.0:07:10.26.0:07:12.96.Default..0.0.0..This friend... you know him?
Dialogue: 0.0:07:14.40.0:07:16.07.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}- Tyler clarendon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:07:18.40.0:07:21.11.Default..0.0.0..This woman outlived\Nboth her kids.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:21.11.0:07:23.87.Default..0.0.0..- His new best friend\Nwas tony chin.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:23.88.0:07:24.98.Default..0.0.0..20.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:24.98.0:07:26.28.Default..0.0.0..Junior at central chicago u.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:26.28.0:07:28.18.Default..0.0.0..No criminal record.\Nbut the last few weeks.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:28.18.0:07:30.88.Default..0.0.0..he suddenly appears all over\Ntyler's social media profile.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:30.88.0:07:32.45.Default..0.0.0..- Mouse. you dump\Nhis phone records?
Dialogue: 0.0:07:32.45.0:07:35.09.Default..0.0.0..- Yeah. there's dozens of calls\Nbetween tyler and tony chin.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:35.09.0:07:36.42.Default..0.0.0..all less than two minutes\Nin duration
Dialogue: 0.0:07:36.42.0:07:38.02.Default..0.0.0..and at all sorts of crazy hours.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:38.02.0:07:40.29.Default..0.0.0..- Have atwater and ruzek\Ntake a run at this guy.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:40.29.0:07:43.23.Default..0.0.0..- You know. uh. tyler...
Dialogue: 0.0:07:43.23.0:07:46.43.Default..0.0.0..He was 2nd battalion.\N7th marine.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:46.43.0:07:47.90.Default..0.0.0..- When?\N- '08.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:47.90.0:07:50.77.Default..0.0.0..He was spitting distance\Nfrom us in kandahar.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:50.77.0:07:53.04.Default..0.0.0..- All right. well.\Nthey saw some action.
Dialogue: 0.0:07:53.04.0:07:54.37.Default..0.0.0..- Yeah. they did.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:06.99.0:08:09.12.Default..0.0.0..- what part of "do not disturb"\Nyou having trouble with?
Dialogue: 0.0:08:09.12.0:08:10.79.Default..0.0.0..- The chicago pd part.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:10.79.0:08:12.29.Default..0.0.0..- Hey.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:12.29.0:08:15.19.Default..0.0.0..Look. I-I...\NI didn't know.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:15.19.0:08:16.36.Default..0.0.0..- It's okay.\NI understand.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:16.36.0:08:17.36.Default..0.0.0..We all look alike.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:17.36.0:08:19.10.Default..0.0.0..- African-americans?
Dialogue: 0.0:08:19.10.0:08:20.20.Default..0.0.0..- Wha...
Dialogue: 0.0:08:20.20.0:08:21.47.Default..0.0.0..- Cops...
Dialogue: 0.0:08:21.47.0:08:23.53.Default..0.0.0..The same cops who heard that
Dialogue: 0.0:08:23.54.0:08:25.84.Default..0.0.0..apparently you're\Nthe guy to talk to.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:25.84.0:08:27.14.Default..0.0.0..- About what?
Dialogue: 0.0:08:27.14.0:08:30.04.Default..0.0.0..- About your buddy\Ntyler right here.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:30.04.0:08:31.78.Default..0.0.0..- I met him at a party I dj'd.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:31.78.0:08:33.08.Default..0.0.0..I didn't know him that well.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:33.08.0:08:34.51.Default..0.0.0..- Really?
Dialogue: 0.0:08:34.51.0:08:35.95.Default..0.0.0..Then why you been calling him\Nday and night?
Dialogue: 0.0:08:35.95.0:08:37.92.Default..0.0.0..- He did a little work for me\Nat the parties.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:37.92.0:08:40.45.Default..0.0.0..providing refreshments.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:40.45.0:08:42.82.Default..0.0.0..- Refreshments. huh?
Dialogue: 0.0:08:42.82.0:08:44.16.Default..0.0.0..- Okay. it's...\NIt's not like that.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:44.16.0:08:46.82.Default..0.0.0..I'm talking beer...\N- tony. please.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:46.83.0:08:49.33.Default..0.0.0..Don't act as stupid as that\Nhaircut makes you look.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:49.33.0:08:51.20.Default..0.0.0..You guys were running\Ndope together.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:51.20.0:08:53.23.Default..0.0.0..Right?\NTony...
Dialogue: 0.0:08:53.23.0:08:54.97.Default..0.0.0..- I... I don't know what\Nyou're talking about.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:54.97.0:08:56.87.Default..0.0.0..I'm a... I'm a phi beta kappa\Nhonor student.
Dialogue: 0.0:08:56.87.0:08:58.54.Default..0.0.0..and I've got a chem midterm\Non Friday. so...
Dialogue: 0.0:08:58.54.0:09:00.44.Default..0.0.0..- let me guess what happened.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:00.44.0:09:03.11.Default..0.0.0..Tyler... he wanted a little bit\Nbigger cut. right?
Dialogue: 0.0:09:03.11.0:09:04.88.Default..0.0.0..So you take a baseball bat...
Dialogue: 0.0:09:04.88.0:09:06.18.Default..0.0.0..Crack him in the head with it.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:08.21.0:09:09.95.Default..0.0.0..- Damn.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:12.67.0:09:16.37.Default..0.0.0..- Hey. officer. do you mind\Nif I grab my wallet?
Dialogue: 0.0:09:16.38.0:09:18.04.Default..0.0.0..I don't want you.\Nyou know. shooting me
Dialogue: 0.0:09:18.04.0:09:19.64.Default..0.0.0..as I reach for it. so...
Dialogue: 0.0:09:23.62.0:09:25.95.Default..0.0.0..Yeah. any more questions.\Ncontact my lawyer.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:25.95.0:09:27.59.Default..0.0.0..- Wow. you have one on retainer.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:27.59.0:09:29.05.Default..0.0.0..- Yeah. this\Nconversation's over.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:31.36.0:09:32.89.Default..0.0.0..- For now.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:34.96.0:09:36.66.Default..0.0.0..- It's never gonna end\Nwith that guy.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:37.11.0:09:39.48.Default..0.0.0..- There's got to be something\Nthat we can do.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:39.76.0:09:41.63.Default..0.0.0..- Private security. I guess?
Dialogue: 0.0:09:42.90.0:09:44.17.Default..0.0.0..- Ride out the year.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:44.17.0:09:46.17.Default..0.0.0..Bid back into 21st legit.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:46.17.0:09:47.94.Default..0.0.0..and then no one can touch you.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:50.44.0:09:51.64.Default..0.0.0..Hey. are you okay?
Dialogue: 0.0:09:51.64.0:09:52.84.Default..0.0.0..Did somebody hurt you?
Dialogue: 0.0:09:52.84.0:09:54.84.Default..0.0.0..- My mom... she hurt my dad\Nreal bad.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:54.84.0:09:56.44.Default..0.0.0..- Call it in.\NWhat's your name. buddy?
Dialogue: 0.0:09:56.45.0:09:57.78.Default..0.0.0..- Chase.\N- 2113. this is an emergency.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:57.78.0:09:58.88.Default..0.0.0..Roll another squad to\N32nd and princeton.
Dialogue: 0.0:09:58.88.0:10:00.01.Default..0.0.0..- You got a last name?
Dialogue: 0.0:10:00.02.0:10:01.12.Default..0.0.0..- Chase. you're gonna be fine.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:01.12.0:10:02.48.Default..0.0.0..We're gonna help your dad.\N- Okay.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:02.49.0:10:03.68.Default..0.0.0..- Hey. look at me.\NWe're gonna help you.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:03.69.0:10:05.65.Default..0.0.0..All right?
Dialogue: 0.0:10:05.66.0:10:07.72.Default..0.0.0..- That's my house.\Nthe one with the flag.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:07.72.0:10:09.09.Default..0.0.0..- Chase. can you stay\Nwith these officers?
Dialogue: 0.0:10:09.09.0:10:10.83.Default..0.0.0..Yeah?\N- Yeah. go in the back.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:15.90.0:10:17.60.Default..0.0.0..- hey.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:20.60.0:10:21.87.Default..0.0.0..- Chicago pd!
Dialogue: 0.0:10:24.67.0:10:26.44.Default..0.0.0..- Clear.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:26.44.0:10:27.71.Default..0.0.0..- Clear.\N- Sir?
Dialogue: 0.0:10:27.71.0:10:29.61.Default..0.0.0..Chicago pd.\NDon't move.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:29.61.0:10:31.88.Default..0.0.0..- Got you. tay.\NComing up behind.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:31.88.0:10:35.72.Default..0.0.0..- Clear.\N- Sir. I need to see your hands.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:35.72.0:10:37.72.Default..0.0.0..Sir. do not move your hands\Nfrom that table!
Dialogue: 0.0:10:37.72.0:10:40.15.Default..0.0.0..Chicago pd!
Dialogue: 0.0:10:40.16.0:10:42.56.Default..0.0.0..- Help me.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:42.56.0:10:43.86.Default..0.0.0..Please.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:43.86.0:10:45.49.Default..0.0.0..I don't want to die.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:46.50.0:10:47.73.Default..0.0.0..Help.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:52.97.0:10:55.40.Default..0.0.0..- Is he gonna be all right?
Dialogue: 0.0:10:55.40.0:10:57.84.Default..0.0.0..- We'll know more\Nwhen we get to med.
Dialogue: 0.0:10:57.84.0:11:00.54.Default..0.0.0..- Where's your mom?
Dialogue: 0.0:11:00.54.0:11:02.68.Default..0.0.0..Hey.\NChase?
Dialogue: 0.0:11:02.68.0:11:04.88.Default..0.0.0..Can you tell me\Nwhere your mom is?
Dialogue: 0.0:11:04.88.0:11:07.05.Default..0.0.0..- I don't know.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:07.05.0:11:08.85.Default..0.0.0..- It's okay.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:08.85.0:11:11.55.Default..0.0.0..Hey. it's okay.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:11.55.0:11:13.69.Default..0.0.0..Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:15.16.0:11:17.63.Default..0.0.0..And that's when your wife\Ngot violent?
Dialogue: 0.0:11:17.63.0:11:21.03.Default..0.0.0..- Yeah. uh. my ex.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:22.93.0:11:26.03.Default..0.0.0..We had words.\NShe went nuts.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:26.04.0:11:29.64.Default..0.0.0..Stabbed me with a steak knife.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:29.64.0:11:31.61.Default..0.0.0..But when she saw the blood.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:31.61.0:11:33.51.Default..0.0.0..she panicked and ran out.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:36.55.0:11:38.18.Default..0.0.0..- She. um...
Dialogue: 0.0:11:38.18.0:11:40.05.Default..0.0.0..She ever do anything\Nlike this before?
Dialogue: 0.0:11:41.05.0:11:42.68.Default..0.0.0..- No.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:42.69.0:11:44.22.Default..0.0.0..Just a lot of bitching.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:45.72.0:11:47.89.Default..0.0.0..But I'll take the knife\Nevery time.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:49.19.0:11:52.76.Default..0.0.0..- And chase was where\Nfor all of this?
Dialogue: 0.0:11:52.76.0:11:55.26.Default..0.0.0..- Napping.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:55.27.0:11:57.97.Default..0.0.0..I couldn't find my phone.
Dialogue: 0.0:11:57.97.0:12:00.70.Default..0.0.0..So I yelled for him.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:00.70.0:12:03.87.Default..0.0.0..He came in.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:03.87.0:12:06.97.Default..0.0.0..He was crying.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:06.98.0:12:09.24.Default..0.0.0..He hugged me.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:11.18.0:12:13.25.Default..0.0.0..That's how come he got\Nblood on him.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:14.88.0:12:17.55.Default..0.0.0..Then he ran to get help.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:17.55.0:12:21.12.Default..0.0.0..- There's no other immediate\Nfamily in chicago?
Dialogue: 0.0:12:21.12.0:12:23.16.Default..0.0.0..- Outside of his mother?\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:23.16.0:12:25.26.Default..0.0.0..- Uh-uh.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:25.26.0:12:27.80.Default..0.0.0..We both moved from st. John.\Nindiana. years ago.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:29.73.0:12:32.57.Default..0.0.0..- All right. well. we put\Nan investigative alert on her.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:33.87.0:12:35.70.Default..0.0.0..Chase...
Dialogue: 0.0:12:35.71.0:12:39.27.Default..0.0.0..Chase'll have to go with dcfs.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:39.28.0:12:41.18.Default..0.0.0..- Can you take him?
Dialogue: 0.0:12:43.98.0:12:47.18.Default..0.0.0..Please?
Dialogue: 0.0:12:47.18.0:12:48.75.Default..0.0.0..Just till I get out of here.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:55.66.0:12:56.66.Default..0.0.0..- You know what. jay?
Dialogue: 0.0:12:56.66.0:12:57.89.Default..0.0.0..It's not your call.
Dialogue: 0.0:12:57.89.0:13:00.76.Default..0.0.0..- I promised that I would\Nlook out for you
Dialogue: 0.0:13:00.76.0:13:01.96.Default..0.0.0..when we came home.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:01.97.0:13:04.07.Default..0.0.0..That is what I'm doing.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:04.07.0:13:06.20.Default..0.0.0..Why are you so insistent\Nthat it has to be right now?
Dialogue: 0.0:13:07.97.0:13:09.27.Default..0.0.0..Take a couple months off.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:09.27.0:13:11.19.Default..0.0.0..Just clear your head.\Nand then if you...
Dialogue: 0.0:13:11.19.0:13:13.11.Default..0.0.0..- no. if I wait. the post will\Nbe gone in six months.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:13.11.0:13:14.21.Default..0.0.0..All right?
Dialogue: 0.0:13:14.21.0:13:15.31.Default..0.0.0..If I don't reenlist now.\Nit's done.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:15.31.0:13:16.61.Default..0.0.0..- Greg. it's a war.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:16.61.0:13:18.18.Default..0.0.0..They're not really\Nturning people away.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:18.18.0:13:20.18.Default..0.0.0..- Do you have any idea\Nwhat it's like?
Dialogue: 0.0:13:20.18.0:13:23.35.Default..0.0.0..I sit behind that desk and watch\Nyou go out every single day...
Dialogue: 0.0:13:23.35.0:13:25.05.Default..0.0.0..Go out and see action.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:25.05.0:13:27.29.Default..0.0.0..Do you have any idea how that\Nactually makes me feel?
Dialogue: 0.0:13:27.29.0:13:28.99.Default..0.0.0..- Then take the police exam!
Dialogue: 0.0:13:28.99.0:13:30.86.Default..0.0.0..- No. I was born\Nto be a soldier!
Dialogue: 0.0:13:30.86.0:13:33.03.Default..0.0.0..A soldier. man!
Dialogue: 0.0:13:34.26.0:13:36.23.Default..0.0.0..If it comes down to it.\NI will die one.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:36.23.0:13:38.10.Default..0.0.0..- Are you crazy?
Dialogue: 0.0:13:39.20.0:13:40.84.Default..0.0.0..Sorry to interrupt.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:40.84.0:13:43.67.Default..0.0.0..Uh. your guy from narcotics.\Nmartinez... he called back.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:43.67.0:13:45.37.Default..0.0.0..They got a line on the dealer\Nwho changed his cut
Dialogue: 0.0:13:45.38.0:13:47.38.Default..0.0.0..from lactose to fentanyl.
Dialogue: 0.0:13:47.38.0:13:49.68.Default..0.0.0..- Thanks.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:08.36.0:14:11.73.Default..0.0.0..- Black ball cap. black hoodie.\Nwhite sneakers.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:11.73.0:14:13.03.Default..0.0.0..- Heavyset guy?
Dialogue: 0.0:14:13.04.0:14:14.40.Default..0.0.0..- Yeah. didn't dig\Nthe nickname "chunk."
Dialogue: 0.0:14:14.40.0:14:16.77.Default..0.0.0..so he took a tire iron\Nto some guy's dome.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:16.77.0:14:17.97.Default..0.0.0..Goes by "red" now.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:17.97.0:14:19.11.Default..0.0.0..Quite the entrepreneur.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:19.11.0:14:20.71.Default..0.0.0..Been working double shifts...
Dialogue: 0.0:14:20.71.0:14:22.04.Default..0.0.0..Managing a spot during the day
Dialogue: 0.0:14:22.05.0:14:23.71.Default..0.0.0..and handling the cut at night.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:23.71.0:14:26.11.Default..0.0.0..- Meaning he knows the source\Nof the supply.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:26.12.0:14:27.25.Default..0.0.0..- Yup.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:30.02.0:14:33.25.Default..0.0.0..- Hey. man. I'm looking for two.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:33.26.0:14:35.26.Default..0.0.0..- Who sent you?
Dialogue: 0.0:14:35.26.0:14:36.72.Default..0.0.0..- Red. come on. man.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:36.73.0:14:39.16.Default..0.0.0..I was here like...\NLike. three weeks ago.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:39.16.0:14:40.93.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}Come on. man.\NCash money.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:14:40.93.0:14:42.76.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}You know I'm good for it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:14:49.14.0:14:51.91.Default..0.0.0..All right.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:51.91.0:14:52.97.Default..0.0.0..We got a positive.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:52.98.0:14:54.04.Default..0.0.0..I repeat. we got a positive.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:54.04.0:14:55.84.Default..0.0.0..Black hat. black hoodie.\Nwhite shoes.
Dialogue: 0.0:14:59.48.0:15:02.35.Default..0.0.0..- Chicago pd.\NLet me see your hands.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:02.35.0:15:03.85.Default..0.0.0..- Hey. red.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:03.85.0:15:06.35.Default..0.0.0..You know who we are.\N- Man. I ain't got nothing.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:07.72.0:15:08.96.Default..0.0.0..- oops.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:08.96.0:15:10.89.Default..0.0.0..Mustache on jackson...
Dialogue: 0.0:15:10.89.0:15:12.19.Default..0.0.0..I drew it.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:12.20.0:15:13.99.Default..0.0.0..My bills.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:21.10.0:15:23.40.Default..0.0.0..- Man. I don't know nothing\Nabout nothing.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:23.41.0:15:27.07.Default..0.0.0..- Bro. if it was me.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:27.08.0:15:28.31.Default..0.0.0..I'd be a hell of a lot\Nmore worried
Dialogue: 0.0:15:28.31.0:15:30.21.Default..0.0.0..about these drug-induced\Nhomicides.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:30.21.0:15:31.48.Default..0.0.0..- I don't even know\Nwhat that is.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:31.48.0:15:32.88.Default..0.0.0..- Nine bodies so far.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:32.88.0:15:34.48.Default..0.0.0..- I didn't serve any\Nof those hypes.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:34.48.0:15:35.48.Default..0.0.0..- It's your dope in 'em.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:35.49.0:15:37.15.Default..0.0.0..Might as well be your bullet.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:41.09.0:15:42.96.Default..0.0.0..- So what you\Nlooking for exactly?
Dialogue: 0.0:15:44.79.0:15:46.39.Default..0.0.0..- You've been inside two years
Dialogue: 0.0:15:46.40.0:15:49.23.Default..0.0.0..and been picked up\Nhow many times?
Dialogue: 0.0:15:49.23.0:15:51.33.Default..0.0.0..Hey.
Dialogue: 0.0:15:52.84.0:15:54.50.Default..0.0.0..What do you think\Nwe're looking for?
Dialogue: 0.0:16:00.34.0:16:03.18.Default..0.0.0..- All right.\Nbut here's the deal.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:05.35.0:16:07.01.Default..0.0.0..I'll give you my supplier.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:07.02.0:16:08.22.Default..0.0.0..but I'm not a rat.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:08.22.0:16:11.32.Default..0.0.0..'cause this dude.\Nhe ain't one of my boys.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:11.32.0:16:13.82.Default..0.0.0..So this don't count as ratting.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:13.82.0:16:15.52.Default..0.0.0..- Makes perfect sense to me.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:15.53.0:16:17.96.Default..0.0.0..- Name's scoot.\NWhite dude.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:17.96.0:16:19.09.Default..0.0.0..- Scoot?
Dialogue: 0.0:16:19.10.0:16:20.93.Default..0.0.0..- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:20.93.0:16:22.20.Default..0.0.0..He's really...
Dialogue: 0.0:16:22.20.0:16:24.30.Default..0.0.0..White.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:26.97.0:16:28.90.Default..0.0.0..- What's he look like?
Dialogue: 0.0:16:28.91.0:16:30.94.Default..0.0.0..- Just a real white dude.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:30.94.0:16:32.41.Default..0.0.0..Wear them lumberjack shirts.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:34.84.0:16:37.18.Default..0.0.0..One time. I went to him.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:37.18.0:16:39.55.Default..0.0.0..I met him at this...\NThis mini-mart.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:39.55.0:16:41.28.Default..0.0.0..- Where?\N- Right off the lake.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:41.28.0:16:43.52.Default..0.0.0..Slid down lsd up north.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:43.52.0:16:45.25.Default..0.0.0..Some rich-ass neighborhood.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:45.25.0:16:46.52.Default..0.0.0..Lawrence or something.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:46.52.0:16:47.99.Default..0.0.0..- All right. when was this?
Dialogue: 0.0:16:47.99.0:16:50.02.Default..0.0.0..- Two mondays ago.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:52.53.0:16:53.96.Default..0.0.0..- Check it out.
Dialogue: 0.0:16:59.04.0:17:00.33.Default..0.0.0..- This is from two weeks ago?
Dialogue: 0.0:17:00.34.0:17:01.80.Default..0.0.0..- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:01.80.0:17:03.27.Default..0.0.0..The black dude...\NNever seen him before.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:03.27.0:17:05.27.Default..0.0.0..That other guy. he comes in\Nhere every other week
Dialogue: 0.0:17:05.27.0:17:08.91.Default..0.0.0..looking for white owl cigars\Nand rolling papers.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:08.91.0:17:10.34.Default..0.0.0..He loves those blunts.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:10.35.0:17:11.85.Default..0.0.0..And you wouldn't believe\Nhow much fuel he burns
Dialogue: 0.0:17:11.85.0:17:13.01.Default..0.0.0..in that boat of his. either.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:13.02.0:17:14.11.Default..0.0.0..- Where can we find him?
Dialogue: 0.0:17:14.12.0:17:16.02.Default..0.0.0..- What'd he do. huh?
Dialogue: 0.0:17:16.02.0:17:18.09.Default..0.0.0..- Parking tickets.\N- Okay.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:18.09.0:17:20.25.Default..0.0.0..I got you.\NI don't know where he lives.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:20.26.0:17:22.22.Default..0.0.0..Uh. but he's got a boat\Nat the marina.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:22.23.0:17:25.23.Default..0.0.0..Uh. just a few days ago I had to\Ntake some propane tanks to him.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:25.23.0:17:26.99.Default..0.0.0..They were having\Nsome kind of rager.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:27.00.0:17:29.56.Default..0.0.0..Yeah. I could show you\Nwhere the slip is at.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:30.57.0:17:32.88.Default..0.0.0..- "whiplash."
Dialogue: 0.0:17:32.88.0:17:35.20.Default..0.0.0..well. there she is.\N- With a gash in the hull.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:35.20.0:17:37.64.Default..0.0.0..What if this wasn't\Na murder at all.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:37.64.0:17:39.47.Default..0.0.0..just a high-speed accident?
Dialogue: 0.0:17:39.48.0:17:42.11.Default..0.0.0..- Either way. we're after\Na fentanyl ring.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:46.58.0:17:48.65.Default..0.0.0..- Waypoints for blind river.\Nontario.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:48.65.0:17:52.02.Default..0.0.0..mackinaw city. michigan.\Nand chicago.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:54.89.0:17:56.99.Default..0.0.0..- We ran a quantitative\Nand qualitative analysis
Dialogue: 0.0:17:56.99.0:17:58.46.Default..0.0.0..on the sample from the lake.
Dialogue: 0.0:17:58.46.0:18:00.29.Default..0.0.0..It's not coming back\Nas fentanyl.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:00.30.0:18:01.43.Default..0.0.0..- What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0.0:18:01.43.0:18:03.33.Default..0.0.0..- Chemically.\Nfentanyl's a pharmaceutical
Dialogue: 0.0:18:03.33.0:18:05.23.Default..0.0.0..designed to treat\Ncancer patients...
Dialogue: 0.0:18:05.23.0:18:09.17.Default..0.0.0..Potent enough that a molecule\Non the head of a pin is deadly.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:09.17.0:18:11.24.Default..0.0.0..but if even\Na molecule's altered.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:11.24.0:18:12.94.Default..0.0.0..then technically. it's not\Na controlled substance.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:12.94.0:18:14.54.Default..0.0.0..That's what I'm talking about.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:14.54.0:18:16.41.Default..0.0.0..- Do you know how many od's\Nwe have off this stuff
Dialogue: 0.0:18:16.41.0:18:17.41.Default..0.0.0..down at med?
Dialogue: 0.0:18:17.41.0:18:18.41.Default..0.0.0..- I do.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:18.41.0:18:20.01.Default..0.0.0..But they od'd on fentanyl
Dialogue: 0.0:18:20.02.0:18:21.42.Default..0.0.0..that had been fully processed.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:21.42.0:18:22.48.Default..0.0.0..The batch you found\Nin the backpack
Dialogue: 0.0:18:22.49.0:18:23.62.Default..0.0.0..hadn't been activated yet.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:23.62.0:18:25.15.Default..0.0.0..which I'm assuming\Nthey were gonna do
Dialogue: 0.0:18:25.15.0:18:26.55.Default..0.0.0..when they got to chicago.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:26.56.0:18:29.22.Default..0.0.0..- So you're saying\Nthat our batch
Dialogue: 0.0:18:29.23.0:18:30.62.Default..0.0.0..is off by a molecule?
Dialogue: 0.0:18:30.63.0:18:32.33.Default..0.0.0..- That is correct.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:35.60.0:18:36.96.Default..0.0.0..- Yeah. I got him.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:36.97.0:18:38.50.Default..0.0.0..They're coming in right now.\NThanks.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:38.50.0:18:40.27.Default..0.0.0..Sarge?
Dialogue: 0.0:18:40.27.0:18:42.07.Default..0.0.0..Sarge. you want to see this.\N- Yeah?
Dialogue: 0.0:18:43.97.0:18:46.11.Default..0.0.0..- High-speed impact\Nwould be consistent
Dialogue: 0.0:18:46.11.0:18:48.28.Default..0.0.0..with blunt force trauma\Nto our vic.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:48.28.0:18:49.69.Default..0.0.0..So I think the owner of the boat
Dialogue: 0.0:18:49.69.0:18:51.11.Default..0.0.0..is the one bringing\Nthe fentanyl in from canada.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:51.11.0:18:53.10.Default..0.0.0..- Mm.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:53.10.0:18:55.08.Default..0.0.0..- Just got the test results\Nback from isp.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:55.08.0:18:57.99.Default..0.0.0..Technically. it's not fentanyl.
Dialogue: 0.0:18:57.99.0:19:00.27.Default..0.0.0..- What?
Dialogue: 0.0:19:00.27.0:19:02.56.Default..0.0.0..- Apparently the manufacturer's\Naltered molecules
Dialogue: 0.0:19:02.56.0:19:04.38.Default..0.0.0..so that this stuff wouldn't be
Dialogue: 0.0:19:04.38.0:19:06.19.Default..0.0.0..on the u.S. Government's\Ncontrolled substance list.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:06.20.0:19:08.00.Default..0.0.0..Until it's activated.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:08.00.0:19:09.30.Default..0.0.0..it's basically baby powder.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:09.30.0:19:12.53.Default..0.0.0..- So we don't have a case?
Dialogue: 0.0:19:25.03.0:19:25.68.Default..0.0.0..- Perfect. thanks.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:25.68.0:19:27.65.Default..0.0.0..- And this. um.\Nis sergeant platt.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:27.65.0:19:28.65.Default..0.0.0..who I've been telling you about.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:28.65.0:19:29.98.Default..0.0.0..- Hey.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:29.99.0:19:31.35.Default..0.0.0..You a hawks fan?
Dialogue: 0.0:19:34.62.0:19:37.46.Default..0.0.0..That's great. because I really\Nneed a wingman
Dialogue: 0.0:19:37.46.0:19:38.99.Default..0.0.0..to keep an eye on this game
Dialogue: 0.0:19:39.00.0:19:40.73.Default..0.0.0..while I'm chained to this desk.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:40.73.0:19:43.20.Default..0.0.0..Will you do that for me?
Dialogue: 0.0:19:43.20.0:19:44.53.Default..0.0.0..- Sure.\N- Thanks.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:44.53.0:19:46.03.Default..0.0.0..Don't forget your shirt.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:46.03.0:19:47.67.Default..0.0.0..Sit right over there. buddy.\N- You got it?
Dialogue: 0.0:19:49.31.0:19:52.64.Default..0.0.0..- kid's mom takes\Na nursing course at lakeside.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:52.64.0:19:54.31.Default..0.0.0..Ends in an hour.
Dialogue: 0.0:19:54.31.0:19:56.18.Default..0.0.0..- Why would someone\Nstab their husband
Dialogue: 0.0:19:56.18.0:19:57.31.Default..0.0.0..and then go to class?
Dialogue: 0.0:19:57.31.0:20:00.05.Default..0.0.0..- 'cause some people\Nare crazy. burgess.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:07.49.0:20:10.06.Default..0.0.0..- Leigh crewes.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:10.06.0:20:11.89.Default..0.0.0..- Yeah?
Dialogue: 0.0:20:11.89.0:20:13.73.Default..0.0.0..- Were you at your ex-husband's\Nplace earlier this morning?
Dialogue: 0.0:20:13.73.0:20:15.26.Default..0.0.0..- Yeah. so?
Dialogue: 0.0:20:15.26.0:20:17.10.Default..0.0.0..- Did you have words with him?
Dialogue: 0.0:20:17.10.0:20:19.47.Default..0.0.0..- he insulted me\Nand screamed at me.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:19.47.0:20:20.60.Default..0.0.0..if that's what you mean.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:20.60.0:20:22.60.Default..0.0.0..- Did it make you mad enough\Nto stab him?
Dialogue: 0.0:20:22.61.0:20:24.17.Default..0.0.0..- What?
Dialogue: 0.0:20:26.04.0:20:27.44.Default..0.0.0..I didn't stab him.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:27.44.0:20:29.54.Default..0.0.0..Gerry's crazy.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:31.18.0:20:33.08.Default..0.0.0..He's been making\Nthreats for years...
Dialogue: 0.0:20:33.08.0:20:34.72.Default..0.0.0..Said he'd do anything\Nto keep chase.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:34.72.0:20:36.72.Default..0.0.0..- Okay. did you ever file\Na restraining order?
Dialogue: 0.0:20:36.72.0:20:38.39.Default..0.0.0..Do you have any paperwork\Nto back this up?
Dialogue: 0.0:20:38.39.0:20:40.19.Default..0.0.0..- No.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:41.36.0:20:43.22.Default..0.0.0..- Ma'am. now is the time\Nto get ahead of this.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:43.23.0:20:44.36.Default..0.0.0..You got to tell us the truth.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:44.36.0:20:45.49.Default..0.0.0..or you're never gonna\Nsee your kid again.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:45.49.0:20:46.49.Default..0.0.0..- No!\N- Whoa.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:46.50.0:20:47.76.Default..0.0.0..- He's not well!
Dialogue: 0.0:20:47.76.0:20:49.10.Default..0.0.0..He's been going through\Na serious depression.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:49.10.0:20:50.10.Default..0.0.0..- I understand that. ma'am.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:50.10.0:20:51.20.Default..0.0.0..Can you put your hands\Non the roof?
Dialogue: 0.0:20:51.20.0:20:52.60.Default..0.0.0..- Uh-uh. no way.\NI didn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:52.60.0:20:54.10.Default..0.0.0..- Ma'am. hands on the roof.\NI understand that.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:54.10.0:20:55.10.Default..0.0.0..Put your hands on the roof.\N- I'm not kidding.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:55.10.0:20:56.27.Default..0.0.0..- We'll sort it out later.
Dialogue: 0.0:20:56.27.0:21:00.11.Default..0.0.0..- I can't believe this!\NIt's okay.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:11.85.0:21:14.39.Default..0.0.0..- Detective olinsky.\N- Ms. Clarendon.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:14.39.0:21:16.26.Default..0.0.0..Hey.\N- Hi.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:16.26.0:21:18.79.Default..0.0.0..Have you...
Dialogue: 0.0:21:18.79.0:21:21.33.Default..0.0.0..Figured out who killed tyler?
Dialogue: 0.0:21:21.33.0:21:23.38.Default..0.0.0..- Not yet.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:23.38.0:21:25.43.Default..0.0.0..But I promise to contact you\Nas soon as we do.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:25.43.0:21:27.40.Default..0.0.0..- At first. I couldn't\Nbring myself
Dialogue: 0.0:21:27.40.0:21:29.34.Default..0.0.0..to go through tyler's things.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:29.34.0:21:33.24.Default..0.0.0..but when I did. I found this.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:33.24.0:21:37.41.Default..0.0.0..He was applying to\Nthe chicago fire department.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:37.41.0:21:41.68.Default..0.0.0..So are you sure he was\Ninvolved in something illegal?
Dialogue: 0.0:21:41.68.0:21:44.75.Default..0.0.0..Because I'm going to have\Nto deal with his loss.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:44.75.0:21:47.32.Default..0.0.0..and knowing that maybe\Nhe turned his life around
Dialogue: 0.0:21:47.32.0:21:49.79.Default..0.0.0..would give me some comfort.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:52.83.0:21:54.86.Default..0.0.0..You can tell me.
Dialogue: 0.0:21:57.27.0:22:00.17.Default..0.0.0..- I'm sorry. but it's looking\Nlike he was involved.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:14.85.0:22:16.92.Default..0.0.0..- Hey. will.\N- Hey. kev.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:16.92.0:22:19.92.Default..0.0.0..- What's up?\N- How you doing on the case?
Dialogue: 0.0:22:19.92.0:22:21.39.Default..0.0.0..- Covering every angle.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:24.49.0:22:27.33.Default..0.0.0..- You got to get this stuff\Noff the streets. jay.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:27.33.0:22:29.33.Default..0.0.0..I just declared\Na 16-year-old girl.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:29.33.0:22:31.23.Default..0.0.0..Sophomore at rutherford high.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:31.23.0:22:33.73.Default..0.0.0..Her mother found out I had\Na brother who's a detective.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:33.74.0:22:35.64.Default..0.0.0..She asked me to give you that.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:37.21.0:22:39.81.Default..0.0.0..I don't mean to push. man.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:39.81.0:22:41.91.Default..0.0.0..I just... I need you to know.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:41.91.0:22:43.38.Default..0.0.0..It's not just career junkies.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:43.38.0:22:44.51.Default..0.0.0..Kids are dying out there.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:44.51.0:22:47.61.Default..0.0.0..- Yeah. Okay.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:47.62.0:22:49.48.Default..0.0.0..All right.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:49.49.0:22:51.29.Default..0.0.0..- Got it?\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:51.29.0:22:54.19.Default..0.0.0..- Sarge. boat's owned by john\Nand christie fitzgerald.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:54.19.0:22:55.62.Default..0.0.0..They're a well-connected\Nchicago couple
Dialogue: 0.0:22:55.62.0:22:57.52.Default..0.0.0..who made a good chunk of change\Nin construction.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:57.53.0:22:58.63.Default..0.0.0..- I just checked with customs.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:58.63.0:22:59.83.Default..0.0.0..As of three days ago.
Dialogue: 0.0:22:59.83.0:23:01.20.Default..0.0.0..they've been on vacation\Nin Italy.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:01.20.0:23:02.46.Default..0.0.0..- Any border crossing to canada?
Dialogue: 0.0:23:02.46.0:23:03.46.Default..0.0.0..- None.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:03.47.0:23:04.67.Default..0.0.0..- But their son. scott.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:04.67.0:23:06.30.Default..0.0.0..attends central chicago u.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:06.30.0:23:07.63.Default..0.0.0..Goes by "scoot."
Dialogue: 0.0:23:07.64.0:23:10.27.Default..0.0.0..he and tony chin were\Nin chem I together.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:10.27.0:23:11.91.Default..0.0.0..- All right. mouse. get me\Na nexus on the phone records
Dialogue: 0.0:23:11.91.0:23:14.37.Default..0.0.0..for him. tony chin. and tyler.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:14.38.0:23:15.94.Default..0.0.0..And have patrol\Npick this scoot up
Dialogue: 0.0:23:15.95.0:23:16.94.Default..0.0.0..and bring him in here.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:16.95.0:23:18.75.Default..0.0.0..I want to talk to that guy.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:31.59.0:23:34.49.Default..0.0.0..You not wanting to be here\Nisn't gonna work either. mouse.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:35.97.0:23:39.27.Default..0.0.0..- I talked to him.\N- I'm not talking to you.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:39.27.0:23:40.87.Default..0.0.0..- You want to stay.\Nthen do your job.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:40.87.0:23:43.80.Default..0.0.0..You don't want to stay.\Nthat's a separate conversation.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:44.81.0:23:46.69.Default..0.0.0..- I've done my job.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:46.69.0:23:48.57.Default..0.0.0..I've done my job since\Nthe day I got here.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:48.58.0:23:49.81.Default..0.0.0..Busted my ass for you.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:49.81.0:23:51.41.Default..0.0.0..I never... never once\Nasked for ot.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:51.41.0:23:53.58.Default..0.0.0..And all I'm asking for\Nis a favor...
Dialogue: 0.0:23:53.58.0:23:55.82.Default..0.0.0..A favor so that maybe\NI can live my life
Dialogue: 0.0:23:55.82.0:23:57.28.Default..0.0.0..the way that I'd like to.
Dialogue: 0.0:23:57.29.0:23:59.45.Default..0.0.0..- Don't go out like this. mouse.
Dialogue: 0.0:24:01.49.0:24:02.89.Default..0.0.0..You've come too far.
Dialogue: 0.0:24:05.36.0:24:06.73.Default..0.0.0..- You know.\Nmaybe voight's right.
Dialogue: 0.0:24:06.73.0:24:08.26.Default..0.0.0..Maybe I just need\Nto clear out of here.
Dialogue: 0.0:24:08.26.0:24:10.33.Default..0.0.0..- What are you gonna do\Nwith your felony record?
Dialogue: 0.0:24:10.33.0:24:11.80.Default..0.0.0..You gonna go back\Nto boosting stereos?
Dialogue: 0.0:24:11.80.0:24:13.27.Default..0.0.0..- That guy on the board...\NThat could've been me
Dialogue: 0.0:24:13.27.0:24:14.64.Default..0.0.0..when I came back here...
Dialogue: 0.0:24:14.64.0:24:16.00.Default..0.0.0..High. doing something\Nstupid and dangerous.
Dialogue: 0.0:24:16.01.0:24:18.27.Default..0.0.0..- Greg. that is not you.\NThat's not you now.
Dialogue: 0.0:24:18.27.0:24:19.71.Default..0.0.0..- I am telling you. jay.
Dialogue: 0.0:24:19.71.0:24:22.54.Default..0.0.0..if I lose my job because\Nof a bender or whatever...
Dialogue: 0.0:24:22.54.0:24:26.28.Default..0.0.0..I'm looking at tyler.\Nand that could've been me.
Dialogue: 0.0:24:26.28.0:24:27.48.Default..0.0.0..It still could be me.
Dialogue: 0.0:24:27.48.0:24:29.78.Default..0.0.0..- No.\N- Hey. hey. guys.
Dialogue: 0.0:24:29.79.0:24:31.32.Default..0.0.0..We're done here.
Dialogue: 0.0:24:31.32.0:24:33.45.Default..0.0.0..Okay?\NWe are on a case.
Dialogue: 0.0:24:33.46.0:24:35.29.Default..0.0.0..Mouse. go back to your desk.
Dialogue: 0.0:24:35.29.0:24:36.69.Default..0.0.0..- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0.0:24:37.89.0:24:40.99.Default..0.0.0..Come on.
Dialogue: 0.0:24:41.00.0:24:42.50.Default..0.0.0..- Hey.\N- I'm. I'm...
Dialogue: 0.0:24:42.50.0:24:44.33.Default..0.0.0..I'm gonna get through to him.
Dialogue: 0.0:24:44.33.0:24:45.97.Default..0.0.0..And he's gonna be all right.
Dialogue: 0.0:24:45.97.0:24:47.73.Default..0.0.0..- Listen.
Dialogue: 0.0:24:47.74.0:24:49.74.Default..0.0.0..What you two went through
Dialogue: 0.0:24:49.74.0:24:53.37.Default..0.0.0..and what you carry is real.
Dialogue: 0.0:24:53.38.0:24:55.48.Default..0.0.0..And you know that if you ever\Nneed my help carrying it.
Dialogue: 0.0:24:55.48.0:24:56.71.Default..0.0.0..you just have to ask me.
Dialogue: 0.0:24:56.71.0:24:58.91.Default..0.0.0..Why are you not\Nlistening to him?
Dialogue: 0.0:24:58.91.0:25:01.38.Default..0.0.0..- Because going back is not\Nthe right move for him.
Dialogue: 0.0:25:01.38.0:25:02.65.Default..0.0.0..- For you.
Dialogue: 0.0:25:02.65.0:25:05.82.Default..0.0.0..Him going back is not\Nthe right move for you.
Dialogue: 0.0:25:07.36.0:25:09.99.Default..0.0.0..But if it was... if you were\Nthe one that wanted to go...
Dialogue: 0.0:25:09.99.0:25:12.59.Default..0.0.0..Would you let anybody\Nstand in your way?
Dialogue: 0.0:25:19.10.0:25:20.97.Default..0.0.0..Come on.
Dialogue: 0.0:25:28.01.0:25:29.01.Default..0.0.0..- How's it going. scoot?
Dialogue: 0.0:25:30.68.0:25:33.35.Default..0.0.0..Mind if I call you scoot?
Dialogue: 0.0:25:33.35.0:25:35.38.Default..0.0.0..- I have no idea why I'm here.
Dialogue: 0.0:25:35.38.0:25:36.62.Default..0.0.0..- Well...
Dialogue: 0.0:25:36.62.0:25:39.99.Default..0.0.0..- We found a boat in\Nyour mom and dad's name.
Dialogue: 0.0:25:39.99.0:25:42.42.Default..0.0.0..It's got a pretty big-sized\Ndent in its hull.
Dialogue: 0.0:25:46.76.0:25:48.03.Default..0.0.0..- Okay.
Dialogue: 0.0:25:51.37.0:25:53.47.Default..0.0.0..Look. I was running bud.
Dialogue: 0.0:25:53.47.0:25:55.00.Default..0.0.0..From canada.
Dialogue: 0.0:25:55.00.0:25:56.90.Default..0.0.0..Super easy.\NNo harm done.
Dialogue: 0.0:25:56.91.0:26:00.11.Default..0.0.0..Just a little\Nrecreational marijuana.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:00.11.0:26:02.74.Default..0.0.0..And then I meet this guy\Ntony chin
Dialogue: 0.0:26:02.75.0:26:04.01.Default..0.0.0..in my class.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:04.01.0:26:05.85.Default..0.0.0..And...
Dialogue: 0.0:26:05.85.0:26:07.68.Default..0.0.0..Yeah. this is him.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:07.68.0:26:09.68.Default..0.0.0..Tony thinks he's a gangster.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:09.69.0:26:11.85.Default..0.0.0..But the real guy is\Nhis uncle. mr. Ng.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:14.69.0:26:16.16.Default..0.0.0..- First name walter?
Dialogue: 0.0:26:16.16.0:26:17.99.Default..0.0.0..- Yeah.\NYeah. him.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:19.76.0:26:22.50.Default..0.0.0..So tony tells him\Nabout our thing.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:22.50.0:26:24.97.Default..0.0.0..Next thing we know.\Nng is sweating us
Dialogue: 0.0:26:24.97.0:26:27.63.Default..0.0.0..to bring in fentanyl\Non the same route.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:27.64.0:26:28.80.Default..0.0.0..And I told tony. "hey. man.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:28.80.0:26:29.87.Default..0.0.0.."I'll drive the boat;
Dialogue: 0.0:26:29.87.0:26:31.57.Default..0.0.0.."I'll get it to the dealers.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:31.57.0:26:33.11.Default..0.0.0..But the other stuff.\Nyou got to figure out."
Dialogue: 0.0:26:33.11.0:26:35.84.Default..0.0.0..so. like. him recruiting the...
Dialogue: 0.0:26:35.84.0:26:38.01.Default..0.0.0..Losers to wear the backpacks?
Dialogue: 0.0:26:38.01.0:26:39.51.Default..0.0.0..That's all him.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:39.52.0:26:41.05.Default..0.0.0..- Losers like tyler.
Dialogue: 0.0:26:48.19.0:26:50.16.Default..0.0.0..These the losers\Nyou're talking about?
Dialogue: 0.0:26:53.50.0:26:55.00.Default..0.0.0..- That night...
Dialogue: 0.0:26:55.00.0:26:56.10.Default..0.0.0..What happened?
Dialogue: 0.0:26:58.93.0:27:00.43.Default..0.0.0..- There was a heavy fog.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:00.44.0:27:01.97.Default..0.0.0..I didn't want to go. I swear.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:01.97.0:27:02.97.Default..0.0.0..- Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:02.97.0:27:05.44.Default..0.0.0..- But ng put a gun on the table.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:07.11.0:27:09.48.Default..0.0.0..I had no choice.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:09.48.0:27:10.91.Default..0.0.0..You don't say no to him.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:12.18.0:27:13.58.Default..0.0.0..I don't. anyway.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:16.79.0:27:19.09.Default..0.0.0..- What did you hit?
Dialogue: 0.0:27:19.09.0:27:23.69.Default..0.0.0..- I guess tyler was seasick.\Nleaning over the edge. and...
Dialogue: 0.0:27:23.69.0:27:26.79.Default..0.0.0..I didn't see the buoy\Nuntil the boat clipped it.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:26.80.0:27:28.53.Default..0.0.0..- This is murder
Dialogue: 0.0:27:28.53.0:27:29.63.Default..0.0.0..we're looking at.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:32.07.0:27:33.97.Default..0.0.0..Maybe...
Dialogue: 0.0:27:33.97.0:27:36.47.Default..0.0.0..Maybe we can leave some of it\Nout of the report.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:36.47.0:27:40.14.Default..0.0.0..but. I mean. you're gonna have\Nto help us take down ng.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:42.74.0:27:45.58.Default..0.0.0..- What do you mean.\Nhelp you bring him down?
Dialogue: 0.0:27:45.58.0:27:48.25.Default..0.0.0..- We set it up.\NYou go in.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:48.25.0:27:49.98.Default..0.0.0..We got eyes on...\N- like. undercover?
Dialogue: 0.0:27:49.99.0:27:52.59.Default..0.0.0..- Correct.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:52.59.0:27:54.09.Default..0.0.0..- Ng is a killer.
Dialogue: 0.0:27:55.99.0:27:59.49.Default..0.0.0..- How long you think you're\Ngonna last at stateville?
Dialogue: 0.0:27:59.50.0:28:01.16.Default..0.0.0..Scoot?
Dialogue: 0.0:28:14.01.0:28:15.64.Default..0.0.0..- You know. what you're\Ngoing through
Dialogue: 0.0:28:15.64.0:28:18.21.Default..0.0.0..is really hard.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:18.21.0:28:20.98.Default..0.0.0..But it is all gonna\Nwork out. okay?
Dialogue: 0.0:28:24.62.0:28:25.89.Default..0.0.0..You know. my mom...
Dialogue: 0.0:28:25.89.0:28:29.76.Default..0.0.0..Boy. she could get\Nreally angry. too.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:29.76.0:28:33.23.Default..0.0.0..But I always knew\Nit wasn't my fault.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:34.86.0:28:37.26.Default..0.0.0..It's important for you\Nto realize that. chase.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:39.60.0:28:42.04.Default..0.0.0..- My dad's the one\Nwho gets real angry.
Dialogue: 0.0:28:58.79.0:29:03.06.Default..0.0.0..- I don't like\Nowing people favors.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:03.06.0:29:04.93.Default..0.0.0..- You and me both.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:04.93.0:29:08.23.Default..0.0.0..- But is it possible to hack\Ninto someone's phone remotely?
Dialogue: 0.0:29:08.23.0:29:09.80.Default..0.0.0..- Uh. technically. yes.\NLegally. no.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:09.80.0:29:11.47.Default..0.0.0..Why?
Dialogue: 0.0:29:11.47.0:29:13.13.Default..0.0.0..- Because this kid\Nburgess and tay picked up
Dialogue: 0.0:29:13.14.0:29:15.24.Default..0.0.0..is about to lose his mom\Non an agg assault charge.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:15.24.0:29:18.34.Default..0.0.0..I need to make sure it went down\Nthe way her ex said it did.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:18.34.0:29:20.94.Default..0.0.0..This is the dad's phone number.\Nname. and dob.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:20.94.0:29:23.84.Default..0.0.0..- Okay. well. I will\Nsee what I can see.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:23.85.0:29:25.21.Default..0.0.0..- Thanks. mouse.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:25.21.0:29:27.91.Default..0.0.0..- Yeah. you got it.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:29.75.0:29:32.19.Default..0.0.0..- Hey.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:32.19.0:29:33.69.Default..0.0.0..- Hey. what's up?
Dialogue: 0.0:29:33.69.0:29:35.92.Default..0.0.0..- Um. listen. man.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:38.93.0:29:41.16.Default..0.0.0..Do whatever it is\Nyou need to do.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:41.16.0:29:43.96.Default..0.0.0..All right?
Dialogue: 0.0:29:43.97.0:29:45.37.Default..0.0.0..I'm behind you...
Dialogue: 0.0:29:45.37.0:29:47.20.Default..0.0.0..100%.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:50.81.0:29:51.91.Default..0.0.0..- Walter ng.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:51.91.0:29:53.81.Default..0.0.0..Hardcore crime boss\Nin chinatown.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:53.81.0:29:55.24.Default..0.0.0..Alleged to be in everything\Nfrom prostitution
Dialogue: 0.0:29:55.24.0:29:56.88.Default..0.0.0..to high-stakes gambling.
Dialogue: 0.0:29:56.88.0:29:59.21.Default..0.0.0..- He's been identified\Nas the source of the fentanyl
Dialogue: 0.0:29:59.21.0:30:01.30.Default..0.0.0..coming into chicago.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:01.30.0:30:03.38.Default..0.0.0..so he is responsible by\Ncoercion for tyler's death.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:03.39.0:30:04.85.Default..0.0.0..- His operation's slick.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:04.85.0:30:07.05.Default..0.0.0..The modified fentanyl\Noriginates in china
Dialogue: 0.0:30:07.06.0:30:10.66.Default..0.0.0..and gets shipped to ng's connect\Nin blind river. ontario.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:10.66.0:30:11.83.Default..0.0.0..And our boy scoot...
Dialogue: 0.0:30:11.83.0:30:13.93.Default..0.0.0..He zips up from the marina.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:13.93.0:30:16.03.Default..0.0.0..Tony chin brings a couple\Nof college kids to mule it down.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:16.03.0:30:19.03.Default..0.0.0..- Marine unit says they put\Noxygen tanks and a gps
Dialogue: 0.0:30:19.03.0:30:20.97.Default..0.0.0..in weighted backpacks\Nalong with the dope.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:20.97.0:30:22.14.Default..0.0.0..If the coast guard rolls up.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:22.14.0:30:24.67.Default..0.0.0..dump the bag.\Ncome back later that night.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:24.67.0:30:26.94.Default..0.0.0..press a button. and boom...\NFloats to the surface.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:26.94.0:30:29.41.Default..0.0.0..- Then from canada.\Nthey head here.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:29.41.0:30:31.41.Default..0.0.0..south of mackinaw city.\Nmichigan.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:31.41.0:30:33.78.Default..0.0.0..They stop to refuel\Nat rowley's bay.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:33.78.0:30:34.91.Default..0.0.0..Then down into chicago.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:34.92.0:30:37.15.Default..0.0.0..- Where scoot gives\Nthe drugs to red
Dialogue: 0.0:30:37.15.0:30:38.65.Default..0.0.0..and several other\Nscumbag dealers.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:38.65.0:30:40.02.Default..0.0.0..and they sell it\Nto kids on the street.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:40.02.0:30:41.39.Default..0.0.0..- We can't touch ng
Dialogue: 0.0:30:41.39.0:30:43.92.Default..0.0.0..because he's modifying\Nthe chemistry of the fentanyl.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:43.93.0:30:46.39.Default..0.0.0..- Yeah. but as soon as he\Nprocesses it here in chicago.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:46.40.0:30:49.26.Default..0.0.0..we can hit him with calculated\Ncriminal drug conspiracy
Dialogue: 0.0:30:49.26.0:30:51.60.Default..0.0.0..and accessory to murder.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:51.60.0:30:53.93.Default..0.0.0..- Any word on why he allows\Nhimself to be called scoot?
Dialogue: 0.0:30:54.94.0:30:56.77.Default..0.0.0..- None yet.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:56.77.0:30:58.37.Default..0.0.0..- Yo. sarge.\Nyou got to see this.
Dialogue: 0.0:30:58.37.0:31:00.27.Default..0.0.0..Scoot made contact.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:01.31.0:31:03.01.Default..0.0.0..- Okay. I'm listening.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:03.01.0:31:05.05.Default..0.0.0..- They're building\Na temporary lab.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:05.05.0:31:06.18.Default..0.0.0..Tony and me are supposed\Nto meet there
Dialogue: 0.0:31:06.18.0:31:07.41.Default..0.0.0..to process the fentanyl.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:07.42.0:31:08.75.Default..0.0.0..- Good. when and where?
Dialogue: 0.0:31:08.75.0:31:10.88.Default..0.0.0..- Tonight.\NLocation tbd.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:10.89.0:31:12.82.Default..0.0.0..Ng's gonna be there. too.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:12.82.0:31:14.82.Default..0.0.0..- He's usually there when\Nyou process the fentanyl?
Dialogue: 0.0:31:15.79.0:31:17.92.Default..0.0.0..- No. but...
Dialogue: 0.0:31:17.93.0:31:19.19.Default..0.0.0..What?
Dialogue: 0.0:31:19.19.0:31:21.06.Default..0.0.0..Now you don't want him?
Dialogue: 0.0:31:21.06.0:31:23.30.Default..0.0.0..Fine. I'll text him...
Dialogue: 0.0:31:23.30.0:31:25.40.Default..0.0.0..Tell him not to show up.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:28.94.0:31:31.24.Default..0.0.0..Ng wants it done. so he'll\Nbe there for pickup.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:36.71.0:31:38.75.Default..0.0.0..- All lined up. sarge.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:40.05.0:31:41.92.Default..0.0.0..- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:43.32.0:31:44.85.Default..0.0.0..- That is a uc phone.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:44.85.0:31:46.29.Default..0.0.0..It looks and acts\Nlike a regular phone.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:46.29.0:31:48.56.Default..0.0.0..so if anybody checks it out.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:48.56.0:31:50.82.Default..0.0.0..they won't be able to tell\Nthat it transmits audio to us.
Dialogue: 0.0:31:51.73.0:31:52.99.Default..0.0.0..- And what's that?
Dialogue: 0.0:31:52.99.0:31:54.36.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}- This is a pinhole camera.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:31:54.36.0:31:56.05.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}Whichever way this is looking{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:31:56.05.0:31:57.73.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}is the way we're\Ngonna be able to see.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:31:57.73.0:31:58.83.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}- Okay.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:32:01.24.0:32:02.97.Default..0.0.0..This guy's gonna kill me.\N- No.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:02.97.0:32:04.44.Default..0.0.0..- He is.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:04.44.0:32:05.90.Default..0.0.0..- Scoot. I know you're\Nout of your element here.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:05.91.0:32:07.77.Default..0.0.0..but we are very much\Nin ours. okay?
Dialogue: 0.0:32:07.78.0:32:09.21.Default..0.0.0..So trust us.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:09.21.0:32:10.38.Default..0.0.0..Relax.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:10.38.0:32:12.25.Default..0.0.0..- okay.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:12.25.0:32:14.11.Default..0.0.0..- Come on.\N- All right.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:30.27.0:32:32.47.Default..0.0.0..- We're through\Nthe south entrance.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:49.38.0:32:50.82.Default..0.0.0..- We're in.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:53.42.0:32:54.85.Default..0.0.0..Switch over.
Dialogue: 0.0:32:58.86.0:33:00.36.Default..0.0.0..We're in position.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:00.36.0:33:01.53.Default..0.0.0..Standing by.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:20.28.0:33:21.55.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}- Mr. Ng sent me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:33:32.43.0:33:34.03.Default..0.0.0..- Okay. there's tony chin.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:34.03.0:33:35.56.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}- Hurry up.\NYou're late.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:33:35.56.0:33:36.90.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}- Everything ready to go?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:33:39.37.0:33:41.43.Default..0.0.0..- Mm. along with some\Ntrigger-pullers.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:48.51.0:33:50.31.Default..0.0.0..- Does anybody see ng?
Dialogue: 0.0:33:50.31.0:33:51.91.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}- Negative.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:33:51.91.0:33:54.05.Default..0.0.0..{\i1}- No. nothing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0.0:33:57.92.0:33:59.09.Default..0.0.0..- There's the buyer.
Dialogue: 0.0:33:59.09.0:34:00.89.Default..0.0.0..- I don't see ng. sarge.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:00.89.0:34:02.59.Default..0.0.0..Do you?
Dialogue: 0.0:34:03.63.0:34:05.02.Default..0.0.0..- Stand by.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:08.56.0:34:10.63.Default..0.0.0..Something's not right.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:10.63.0:34:12.13.Default..0.0.0..- All right.\Nbut the converted fentanyl's
Dialogue: 0.0:34:12.13.0:34:13.47.Default..0.0.0..about to walk out the door.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:18.47.0:34:20.57.Default..0.0.0..- He's leaving.\NGot to go now.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:20.58.0:34:21.91.Default..0.0.0..- Move in.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:21.91.0:34:22.91.Default..0.0.0..Go. Go!
Dialogue: 0.0:34:22.91.0:34:24.64.Default..0.0.0..- Chicago pd!\NNobody move!
Dialogue: 0.0:34:24.65.0:34:26.38.Default..0.0.0..- Chicago pd!\NGet back!
Dialogue: 0.0:34:26.38.0:34:27.66.Default..0.0.0..- Don't move! Don't move!\N- Stop!
Dialogue: 0.0:34:28.92.0:34:30.15.Default..0.0.0..- chicago pd!\NEverybody's hands. now!
Dialogue: 0.0:34:30.15.0:34:31.35.Default..0.0.0..- Now. now!\N- Back it up!
Dialogue: 0.0:34:31.35.0:34:32.55.Default..0.0.0..- Get down on the ground!\N- Walk this way.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:32.55.0:34:34.25.Default..0.0.0..- Get on the ground!\N- Walk this way.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:34.26.0:34:37.12.Default..0.0.0..- Keep your hands spread out!\N- Get on the ground!
Dialogue: 0.0:34:37.13.0:34:39.46.Default..0.0.0..- Police! Freeze!\NTurn around!
Dialogue: 0.0:34:39.46.0:34:41.53.Default..0.0.0..Turn around.\NTurn around.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:41.53.0:34:43.10.Default..0.0.0..- Don't look at me.\NLook at the ground!
Dialogue: 0.0:34:43.10.0:34:44.50.Default..0.0.0..- Don't move!
Dialogue: 0.0:34:44.50.0:34:46.07.Default..0.0.0..- drop it!
Dialogue: 0.0:34:46.07.0:34:47.33.Default..0.0.0..On your knees.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:49.10.0:34:50.38.Default..0.0.0..Get down.\NHands behind your back.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:55.69.0:34:56.38.Default..0.0.0..- Man. why are you cuffing me?
Dialogue: 0.0:34:56.38.0:34:57.48.Default..0.0.0..I did what you guys asked.
Dialogue: 0.0:34:57.48.0:34:58.95.Default..0.0.0..- I knew it. you piece of sh...
Dialogue: 0.0:34:58.95.0:35:00.75.Default..0.0.0..- Shut your mouth.\N- You're on your own. dude.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:04.49.0:35:06.49.Default..0.0.0..- Tony chin.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:06.49.0:35:07.59.Default..0.0.0..Stand him up.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:09.99.0:35:11.32.Default..0.0.0..Where's your uncle?
Dialogue: 0.0:35:11.33.0:35:12.56.Default..0.0.0..He's supposed to be here.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:12.56.0:35:14.23.Default..0.0.0..- I don't know what\Nyou're talking about.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:14.23.0:35:16.03.Default..0.0.0..- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:16.03.0:35:17.40.Default..0.0.0..Well. kid. guess what.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:17.40.0:35:19.60.Default..0.0.0..You got caught holding the bag.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:19.60.0:35:23.34.Default..0.0.0..Murder. calculated criminal\Ndrug conspiracy.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:23.34.0:35:24.47.Default..0.0.0..Haul him in.
Dialogue: 0.0:35:56.10.0:35:57.97.Default..0.0.0..- You can't park there.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:04.68.0:36:07.31.Default..0.0.0..- Sergeant voight\Nto see walter ng.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:08.52.0:36:10.22.Default..0.0.0..Open that door.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:11.75.0:36:13.45.Default..0.0.0..- This way.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:15.29.0:36:16.66.Default..0.0.0..- Policeman coming your way.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:26.43.0:36:27.60.Default..0.0.0..- What's up. walter?
Dialogue: 0.0:36:27.60.0:36:29.67.Default..0.0.0..- Sergeant.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:31.74.0:36:34.11.Default..0.0.0..- Let me get this straight.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:34.11.0:36:37.04.Default..0.0.0..You served up your own nephew?
Dialogue: 0.0:36:37.05.0:36:39.18.Default..0.0.0..Man. isn't that against\Nsome kind of...
Dialogue: 0.0:36:39.18.0:36:41.11.Default..0.0.0..Tradition or something?
Dialogue: 0.0:36:41.12.0:36:42.12.Default..0.0.0..- Tony?
Dialogue: 0.0:36:42.12.0:36:43.32.Default..0.0.0..Is that who you're\Ntalking about?
Dialogue: 0.0:36:43.32.0:36:44.48.Default..0.0.0..- Mm.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:44.49.0:36:45.65.Default..0.0.0..- Tony's had a drug\Nand alcohol problem
Dialogue: 0.0:36:45.65.0:36:47.09.Default..0.0.0..for years now.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:47.09.0:36:49.22.Default..0.0.0..Gets to a point where\Nyou just. uh.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:49.22.0:36:50.66.Default..0.0.0..stop answering the phone.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:52.13.0:36:54.46.Default..0.0.0..- I got to admit...
Dialogue: 0.0:36:54.46.0:36:56.33.Default..0.0.0..We really thought we\Nhad you this time.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:56.33.0:36:58.16.Default..0.0.0..- Whatever that means.
Dialogue: 0.0:36:58.17.0:37:02.34.Default..0.0.0..- It means you keep running\Nyour illegal card games.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:02.34.0:37:06.14.Default..0.0.0..counterfeit watches.\Nmassage parlors.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:06.14.0:37:08.51.Default..0.0.0..You take your chances;\Nwe'll take ours.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:09.54.0:37:11.74.Default..0.0.0..But if you pump any more\Nfentanyl into my city.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:11.75.0:37:14.68.Default..0.0.0..they're gonna be pulling\Nyou out of the river.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:14.68.0:37:16.15.Default..0.0.0..You understand?
Dialogue: 0.0:37:17.29.0:37:18.45.Default..0.0.0..- Sure.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:25.66.0:37:27.59.Default..0.0.0..- That was a yes or no question.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:30.10.0:37:31.70.Default..0.0.0..- Yes.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:31.70.0:37:33.33.Default..0.0.0..I understand.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:46.82.0:37:49.25.Default..0.0.0..- I tunneled in on\Nthat dude's cell phone.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:49.25.0:37:51.22.Default..0.0.0..There's something you\Nshould take a look at.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:53.69.0:37:56.52.Default..0.0.0..- Oh. lord.
Dialogue: 0.0:37:56.52.0:37:58.52.Default..0.0.0..Will you send that\Nto burgess and tay?
Dialogue: 0.0:37:58.53.0:38:00.66.Default..0.0.0..- Sure.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:00.66.0:38:03.63.Default..0.0.0..- And. um. I heard\Nyou were looking
Dialogue: 0.0:38:03.63.0:38:05.40.Default..0.0.0..to get a felony disappeared.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:11.67.0:38:13.24.Default..0.0.0..- I mean. how did you even...
Dialogue: 0.0:38:13.24.0:38:14.41.Default..0.0.0..- jay told me.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:22.88.0:38:26.42.Default..0.0.0..- 17 google searches on\Na "journal of medicine" study
Dialogue: 0.0:38:26.42.0:38:29.32.Default..0.0.0..about non-fatal stab wounds?
Dialogue: 0.0:38:29.32.0:38:30.86.Default..0.0.0..- What?
Dialogue: 0.0:38:30.86.0:38:33.29.Default..0.0.0..Were you monitoring my phone?
Dialogue: 0.0:38:33.29.0:38:34.51.Default..0.0.0..Is that even legal?
Dialogue: 0.0:38:34.51.0:38:35.73.Default..0.0.0..- You said your ex\Nstabbed you in the neck.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:35.73.0:38:37.63.Default..0.0.0..but your wound's not\Nconsistent with that.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:37.63.0:38:39.83.Default..0.0.0..She's 5'6".\NYou're what. 6'3"?
Dialogue: 0.0:38:39.83.0:38:41.33.Default..0.0.0..- I was sitting down.\N- Oh.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:41.34.0:38:43.67.Default..0.0.0..- You do a lot of arguing\Nsitting down. jerry?
Dialogue: 0.0:38:43.67.0:38:46.31.Default..0.0.0..- Look. you lost it.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:46.31.0:38:48.57.Default..0.0.0..You did a crazy thing.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:48.58.0:38:50.18.Default..0.0.0..But if you ever want\Nto see your boy again.
Dialogue: 0.0:38:50.18.0:38:51.81.Default..0.0.0..now is the time\Nto tell the truth.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:02.86.0:39:04.82.Default..0.0.0..- Nine years of marriage.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:05.89.0:39:08.26.Default..0.0.0..I gave up my job\Nso I could stay home
Dialogue: 0.0:39:08.26.0:39:09.70.Default..0.0.0..and take care of chase.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:10.90.0:39:13.57.Default..0.0.0..And she walks out\Nfor a classmate.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:14.47.0:39:17.47.Default..0.0.0..I gave her everything.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:17.47.0:39:19.67.Default..0.0.0..And now she won't\Neven talk to me.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:27.88.0:39:30.28.Default..0.0.0..- So your mom never\Nhurt your dad.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:30.29.0:39:31.28.Default..0.0.0..You know that. right?
Dialogue: 0.0:39:31.29.0:39:33.49.Default..0.0.0..- Yeah.\N- Okay.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:33.49.0:39:35.49.Default..0.0.0..'cause I have somebody\Nhere to see you.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:35.49.0:39:36.56.Default..0.0.0..- Hi.\N- Mom!
Dialogue: 0.0:39:36.56.0:39:38.69.Default..0.0.0..- Oh. sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:38.69.0:39:41.49.Default..0.0.0..We're going home. sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:41.50.0:39:43.43.Default..0.0.0..Thank you.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:43.43.0:39:44.90.Default..0.0.0..- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0.0:39:44.90.0:39:46.90.Default..0.0.0..- So then who hurt my dad?
Dialogue: 0.0:39:49.60.0:39:51.80.Default..0.0.0..- We'll talk about this.\NWe got to go.
Dialogue: 0.0:40:10.96.0:40:12.79.Default..0.0.0..- Hi.\N- Yes?
Dialogue: 0.0:40:14.40.0:40:17.73.Default..0.0.0..- So. uh. tyler can be\Nburied next to grace.
Dialogue: 0.0:40:24.41.0:40:27.51.Default..0.0.0..- okay.
Dialogue: 0.0:40:33.01.0:40:34.88.Default..0.0.0..- Look.
Dialogue: 0.0:40:34.88.0:40:37.72.Default..0.0.0..It's really easy for a woman\Nto catch a rep on this job.
Dialogue: 0.0:40:37.72.0:40:39.95.Default..0.0.0..whether or not you deserve it.
Dialogue: 0.0:40:39.95.0:40:42.52.Default..0.0.0..It looks like I'm never gonna\Nget the chance to...
Dialogue: 0.0:40:45.56.0:40:48.56.Default..0.0.0..Go after what you want. kim.
Dialogue: 0.0:40:48.56.0:40:49.86.Default..0.0.0..Don't wait.
Dialogue: 0.0:41:08.58.0:41:09.68.Default..0.0.0..- Come on in.
Dialogue: 0.0:41:12.42.0:41:13.99.Default..0.0.0..- Sergeant.
Dialogue: 0.0:41:13.99.0:41:16.72.Default..0.0.0..- Yeah?
Dialogue: 0.0:41:16.72.0:41:19.03.Default..0.0.0..- I just wanted to...
Dialogue: 0.0:41:19.03.0:41:21.43.Default..0.0.0..I just wanted to reiterate\Nmy desire and my commitment
Dialogue: 0.0:41:21.43.0:41:23.70.Default..0.0.0..to one day be detailed\Nup to intelligence.
Dialogue: 0.0:41:25.57.0:41:27.30.Default..0.0.0..I know that it was\Noffered once before.
Dialogue: 0.0:41:27.30.0:41:31.07.Default..0.0.0..but I felt that I still had\Nsomething to learn in patrol.
Dialogue: 0.0:41:31.07.0:41:32.57.Default..0.0.0..And I'm glad that I stayed.
Dialogue: 0.0:41:32.57.0:41:34.47.Default..0.0.0..Yeah.
Dialogue: 0.0:41:34.48.0:41:36.88.Default..0.0.0..But if the opportunity ever\Npresented itself again.
Dialogue: 0.0:41:36.88.0:41:39.61.Default..0.0.0..I... I just want you to know
Dialogue: 0.0:41:39.61.0:41:41.88.Default..0.0.0..that it would be the best\Ndecision that you ever made
Dialogue: 0.0:41:41.88.0:41:44.45.Default..0.0.0..to have me be a part\Nof your unit.
Dialogue: 0.0:41:50.76.0:41:53.49.Default..0.0.0..That's all.
Dialogue: 0.0:41:53.49.0:41:55.59.Default..0.0.0..- Be ready.
Dialogue: 0.0:41:57.10.0:41:58.40.Default..0.0.0..- I will.
Dialogue: 0.0:41:58.40.0:42:00.50.Default..0.0.0..I am.
